",\"position\":1,\"values\":[\"Blush\",\"Charcoal\",\"Sage\",\"Sand\",\"Sea\"]}]},{\"id\":8308715520135,\"title\":\"Bootstrap Empire Book\",\"handle\":\"bootstrap-empire-book\",\"body_html\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThe Bala Blueprint for Building a $100M Brand from the Ground Up\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eThe Definitive Guide to Building a Viral Brand From Scratch, by Natalie Holloway, co-founder of Bala delivers the ultimate guide to successfully transforming your best business idea into a thriving enterprise. The book is a start-to-finish playbook where you'll discover: \\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eHow to pitch, budget, finance, market, and hire for your new company.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eA comprehensive roadmap to growing your new company, including the mindset, toolkit, step-by-step guidance, and long-term strategy necessary to make your idea a reality.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eHands-on techniques for bootstrapping your business, with or without existing funding, and strategies for demolishing common obstacles to success.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eSpecific tips for how to conduct early-stage marketing, knowing when to start hiring, how to pitch effectively, and how to take advantage of momentum.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003ePerfect for aspiring entrepreneurs and founders, Bootstrap Empire is a must-read guide for everyone interested in finding the most effective and efficient way to entrepreneurial success.\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\",\"published_at\":\"2026-01-07T09:31:13-08:00\",\"created_at\":\"2025-12-22T09:36:54-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T06:40:37-07:00\",\"vendor\":\"Bala\",\"product_type\":\"\",\"tags\":[],\"variants\":[{\"id\":43663884714119,\"title\":\"Default Title\",\"option1\":\"Default Title\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"BE-NA-SEA\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":null,\"ava