\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eKnock out your workouts with Bala Boxing Gloves, the chicest gloves in the game. Whether you’re a rookie or a seasoned vet, these ring-ready gloves will help build strength and endurance with each and every punch. \\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003ePart of a limited-edition Ralph Lauren Pink Pony capsule, 25% of the purchase price helps benefit programs for cancer screenings, early treatment, research and patient navigation. To learn more, please visit \\u003ca href=\\\"http:\\/\\/RalphLauren.com\\/PinkPony\\\"\\u003eRalphLauren.com\\/PinkPony\\u003c\\/a\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eMade of the highest quality fitness materials – a leather shell and polyester lining. Hook and loop fasteners allow for a perfect fit every time.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eIncludes 2x 14oz gloves. \\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eTo clean, gently wipe with a soft, water-soaked cloth. Do not use wet wipes, alcohol or other liquids. Do not expose gloves to prolonged sunlight.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eProduct Dimensions: 11” x 7 ¾” x 6” per Glove\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\",\"published_at\":\"2024-09-25T09:40:57-07:00\",\"created_at\":\"2024-09-25T08:45:43-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T06:40:37-07:00\",\"vendor\":\"Bala\",\"product_type\":\"\",\"tags\":[\"collab\",\"flex-hsa\"],\"variants\":[{\"id\":41956369956999,\"title\":\"Black\",\"option1\":\"Black\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"BG-PP-POBK\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":{\"id\":32629987967111,\"product_id\":7903558336647,\"position\":2,\"created_at\":\"2024-09-24T16:12:50-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2024-09-24T16:12:52-07:00\",\"alt\":null,\"width\":1200,\"height\":1500,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.shopify.com\\/s\\/files\\/1\\/0007\\/81